Facebook: Mercurial (some use GIT through a bridge;
gmane.org
according to Joshua Redstone GIT is fairly widely used as well)
Yahoo!: SVN and Git
Zynga: SVN and GIT
Quora: Git
Twitter: Git
eBay: IBM Clear Case, Git
Salesforce: Perforce and Git
VMware: Perforce
NetApp: Perforce
SAP: Perforce
Google: Perforce-like (with custom wrapper "g4"), git (Chrome, Android)
Amazon: Perforce is the most widely used, although Git recently became the recommended source control system
Apple: each team may choose which tool to use; SVN, Mercurial, GIT, and even CVS are used
Microsoft: Perforce-like (Source Depot), Git, TFS
